dc_title_s: Commissioners official railway map of Missouri. Completed to January 1st 1888. Copyright 1887 by R.T. Higgins
dc_description_s: Shows relief by hachures, drainage, names river valleys, indicates cities and towns, county boundaries, and the railroad network by distinguishing colors.|LC also has 1898 edition measuring 71 x 83 cm.; Description derived from published bibliography.|47 x 53 centimeters|Scale approximately 1:150,000|General Map Collection
